org.universAAL.middleware.managers.configuration.core.impl.secondaryManagers

Class ConfigurationEditorPool

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.universAAL.middleware.managers.configuration.core.impl.secondaryManagers.ConfigurationEditorPool

  • public class ConfigurationEditorPool
extends Object
    This secondary manager is used to create, and manage all the ConfigurableEntityEditors that need to be created. WeakReference is used, so when the editors are no longer used they automatically de register. If a ConfigurableEntityEditor is not yet referenced, then it is created (depending on the type of the Editor needed file VS parameter and Local VS remote).
    Author:
    amedrano
